00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:26,957
<i>When you very much
want something to be true...</i>

488
00:28:26,958 --> 00:28:27,874
- Huh.
- Hmm.

489
00:28:27,875 --> 00:28:31,582
<i>...it's very easy
to convince yourself that it is.</i>

490
00:28:31,583 --> 00:28:34,457
Hi there, Mr. and Mrs. Twit.
Name's Dee Dumdie-Dungle.

491
00:28:34,458 --> 00:28:37,332
