- Horvis Dungle!

492
00:28:37,333 --> 00:28:38,915
Yeah, that's your name, hon.

493
00:28:38,916 --> 00:28:41,915
He seems to think Twitlandia
could make Triperot

494
00:28:41,916 --> 00:28:43,832
the fun capital of the world again.

495
00:28:43,833 --> 00:28:46,832
And I'm like, "Hmm..."

496
00:28:46,833 --> 00:28:48,999
Yeah, she's always like, "Hmm..."

497
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,082
Uh, but I'm more like, "Hmm!"

498
00:28:51,083 --> 00:28:53,957
So anyhow, uh,
we called a few of our friends

499
00:28:53,958 --> 00:28:55,457
to help bail you guys out.

500
00:28:55,458 --> 00:28:56,832
Yeah.

501
00:28:56,833 --> 00:29:00,332
Because if Twitlandia is for real,
boy, we all want in.

502
00:29:00,333 --> 00:29:02,791
I also want in, also as well.

503
00:29:03,458 --> 00:29:04,415
You hear that?

504
00:29:04,416 --> 00:29:06,332
I do.

505
00:29:06,333 --> 00:29:09,915
I'd say it's high time
we start making some promises

506
