we have no intention of keeping.

507
00:29:13,958 --> 00:29:16,374
Yes, my friends, it's true.

508
00:29:16,375 --> 00:29:19,707
If we reopen Twitlandia,
tourism will return,

509
00:29:19,708 --> 00:29:22,915
Triperot will be
the fun capital of the world again,

510
00:29:22,916 --> 00:29:26,415
and all the city's problems
will be solved.

511
00:29:26,416 --> 00:29:30,540
But none of that can happen
without one little thing.

512
00:29:30,541 --> 00:29:31,665
Your money.

513
00:29:31,666 --> 00:29:35,999
And that is why we've got
a honey of a deal for you.

514
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:39,124
If you invest just $1,000,

515
00:29:39,125 --> 00:29:42,415
we guarantee you $1 billion

516
00:29:42,416 --> 00:29:43,999
when the park opens.

517
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,207
Holy smokes.

518
00:29:45,208 --> 00:29:46,665
That's a great deal.

519
00:29:46,666 --> 00:29:49,583
Yeah, we can just dip
into Dorcas's college fund.

520
00:29:50,208 --> 00:29:53,582
Uh, Mom, Dad, a moment of your time.

521
00:29:53,583 --> 00:29:56,707
This seems like an obvious lie.

522
00:29:56,708 --> 00:30:00,249
Oh, Dorcas,
you're just too young to understand

523
