- Hurry, Beesh!

584
00:35:06,958 --> 00:35:10,457
- Go. Don't let them catch you.
- Those monsters will kill you.

585
00:35:10,458 --> 00:35:13,707
- Don't say "kill." It's negative.
- Come on, Beesh. Hurry.

586
00:35:13,708 --> 00:35:16,040
- Save yourselves.
- Hurry!

587
00:35:16,041 --> 00:35:17,375
