600
00:36:18,250 --> 00:36:20,457
Hi, Mr. Napkin. Everything's fine.

601
00:36:20,458 --> 00:36:24,540
Whatever you do,
do not open the door for the Twits.

602
00:36:24,541 --> 00:36:27,416
You got it, Beesha.
Don't open the door for the Twits.

603
00:36:30,666 --> 00:36:32,957
Welcome to the Triperot Home for Children.

604
00:36:32,958 --> 00:36:34,415
What can I do you for?

605
00:36:34,416 --> 00:36:35,832
Where are they?

606
