over a hot beef loaf

613
00:36:53,791 --> 00:36:55,458
and some spray cheese.

614
00:36:58,291 --> 00:37:01,665
Beesha, he let them in,
and he offered them cheese!

615
00:37:01,666 --> 00:37:03,665
