Come on, everyone. Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

648
00:38:52,916 --> 00:38:54,750
Okay. Okay.

649
00:38:58,958 --> 00:39:01,166
- Hurry, Harold.
- Let's go! Come on!

650
00:39:11,958 --> 00:39:14,166
Action positions now!

651
00:39:23,375 --> 00:39:26,458
Go on.
That burning sensation in your chest...

652
00:39:27,458 --> 00:39:28,290
...is natural.

653
00:39:28,291 --> 00:39:32,749
- Okay, you brats. We want what's ours.
- Thank goodness you're here.

654
00:39:32,750 --> 00:39:36,499
- They went right through that door.
- They're sneaky little critters.

655
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:38,833
- Ooh!
- Move it! What are you waiting for?

656
00:39:57,125 --> 00:39:58,124
Gotta admit...

657
00:39:58,125 --> 00:40:01,040
...that trick was pretty brilliant.

658
00:40:01,041 --> 00:40:02,290
And professional.

659
00:40:02,291 --> 00:40:03,375
Ouch!

660
00:40:04,333 --> 00:40:05,665
Are you okay?

661
00:40:05,666 --> 00:40:07,707
You little sneaks!

662
00:40:07,708 --> 00:40:09,625
I gotta lock the door.

663
00:40:17,416 --> 00:40:19,833
Sorry about that. That's on me.

664
00:40:21,208 --> 00:40:23,083
Here I go again, bumbling Burl.

665
00:40:40,375 --> 00:40:43,707
Hey, little girl. Little girl?

666
00:40:43,708 --> 00:40:45,790
Mm, you're good.

667
00:40:45,791 --> 00:40:47,624
You're very good.

668
00:40:47,625 --> 00:40:50,582
You tricked us with your hidden camera.
Got us locked up.

669
00:40:50,583 --> 00:40:52,624
Then stole our stolen Muggle-Wumps.

670
00:40:52,625 --> 00:40:55,165
Then you tricked us
with that pretend door.

671
00:40:55,166 --> 00:40:59,374
You are a Twit in the making,
is what you are.

672
00:40:59,375 --> 00:41:00,707
