<i>How far we've come</i>

1457
01:31:16,541 --> 01:31:17,583
No!

1458
01:31:26,791 --> 01:31:28,332
What?

1459
01:31:28,333 --> 01:31:30,375
Huh?

1460
01:31:32,333 --> 01:31:35,125
Where on earth are we?

1461
01:31:37,833 --> 01:31:39,375
It looks like...

1462
01:31:40,291 --> 01:31:41,208
Loompaland.

1463
01:31:44,041 --> 01:31:46,833
I don't like this. Not one little bit.

1464
01:31:52,000 --> 01:31:54,207
- Mm.
- I knew it would end like this.

1465
01:31:54,208 --> 01:31:57,291
- This is your fault!
- It's your fault, you dung beetle.

1466
01:32:12,250 --> 01:32:16,166
<i>Every day I fall in love with you</i>

1467
01:32:16,875 --> 01:32:19,416
<i>And then you hurt me</i>

1468
01:32:20,333 --> 01:32:22,958
<i>Splitting my heart in two</i>

1469
01:32:23,541 --> 01:32:29,291
<i>But then I fall once again</i>

1470
01:32:32,500 --> 01:32:36,291
<i>Well, I bought you a diamond ring</i>

1471
01:32:37,041 --> 01:32:39,750
<i>Then later you pawned it</i>

